{"text_id":192653,"tokens":["The"," image"," of"," Gal","lic"," warriors"," as"," undis","cipl","ined",","," shirt","less"," barbarians"," is"," a"," stereotype"," that"," has"," been"," perpetuated"," by"," centuries"," of"," Roman"," propaganda"," and"," popular"," culture","."," While"," it","'","s"," true"," that"," Gal","lic"," warriors"," were"," known"," for"," their"," individual"," bravery"," and"," fer","ocity",","," the"," reality"," is"," more"," nuanced",".","\n\n","Firstly",","," it","'","s"," important"," to"," note"," that"," the"," Ga","uls"," were"," not"," a"," single",","," monolithic"," entity",","," but"," rather"," a"," collection"," of"," tribes"," and"," feder","ations"," with"," their"," own"," distinct"," cultures",","," social"," structures",","," and"," military"," traditions","."," The"," Ga","uls"," that"," Caesar"," faced"," during"," his"," campaigns"," in"," Gaul"," (","modern","-","day"," France"," and"," Belgium",")"," were"," a"," complex"," and"," diverse"," people",","," with"," a"," rich"," cultural"," heritage"," and"," a"," long"," history"," of"," interaction"," with"," the"," Mediterranean"," world",".","\n\n","In"," terms"," of"," military"," organization",","," a"," Gal","lic"," war","host"," was"," typically"," organized"," around"," a"," core"," of"," noble"," warriors",","," who"," were"," often"," equipped"," with"," high","-","quality"," armor",","," including"," helmets",","," swords",","," and"," shields","."," These"," warriors"," were"," often"," accompanied"," by"," lighter","-","armed"," infantry"," and"," cavalry",","," who"," were"," drawn"," from"," the"," lower"," social"," classes","."," The"," Ga","uls"," were"," also"," known"," to"," employ"," mercenary"," troops",","," including"," archers"," and"," sling","ers",","," who"," were"," recruited"," from"," neighboring"," tribes"," or"," regions",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," key"," features"," of"," Gal","lic"," warfare"," was"," the"," use"," of"," ch